Ijeoma Josephina Otabor (amụrụ na 2 June 1997) nke a maara dị ka Phyna bụ onye Naijiria na-eme ihe nkiri, ihe nlereanya, nwanyị na-eme ka mmadụ na onye na-eme TV. Ọ bụ onye mmeri nke Big Brother Naija oge 7.
Phyna si Edo State, mana a mụrụ ya na Lagos State. Ọ tolitere na Edo State ebe ọ gụrụ akwụkwọ. Ọ gụsịrị akwụkwọ na Injinia na Auchi Polytechnic
Tupu ọ banye n'ụlọ Big Brother Naija, Phyna bụ onye na-ere ahịa, onye malitere ọrụ ya na kọleji ma ụlọ ọrụ na-emepụta ihe bịanyere aka na ya...
Phyna banyere n'oge nke asaa nke Big Brother Naija (Level Up) dị ka onye nke iri na 23 Julaị 2022.

N'oge ngwụcha oge nke ihe ngosi ahụ na 2 Ọktoba 2022, a mara ya dị ka onye mmeri na-enweta 40.74% nke votu ikpeazụ n'ihu Bryann na 26.74% nke ngụkọta vootu a tụbara ma nwee ikike inweta nnukwu ihe nrite nke Ō100 000 000 (otu narị nde naira), na-eme ka ọ bụrụ nwanyị nke abụọ meriri ihe ngosi ahụ, afọ atọ mgbe Mercy Eke meriri ya.
